column2: SELECT ALL   p.objID, p.RA, p.DEC,     p.petroMag_u as u,   p.petroMagErr_u as u_err,   p.petroMag_g as g,   p.petroMagErr_g as g_err,   p.petroMag_r as r,   p.petroMagErr_r as r_err,   p.petroMag_i as i,   p.petroMagErr_i as i_err,   p.petroMag_z as z,    p.petroMagErr_z as z_err,   s.z as z_red,   s.zErr as z_red_err,   TM.J_M_K2#FE as J,    TM.J_MSIG_K2#FE as J_err,   TM.H_M_K2#FE as H,    TM.H_MSIG_K2#FE as H_err,   TM.K_M_K2#FE as K,    TM.K_MSIG_K2#FE as K_err    into mydb.crossMatchsurveys from PhotoObj AS p    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid   JOIN TwoMassXSC AS TM ON TM.objid = p.objid      JOIN GalexGR6.xSDSSDR7 as G6 ON G6.SDSSobjid = p.objid    WHERE     p.petroMag_r <#    AND p.petroMag_g <#   AND p.petroMag_u <#   AND s.class=&&&    AND s.z>#   AND s.z<#
